usdIsisAgent.name: usdIsisAgent

revisions.description: The initial release of this management information module.

usdIsisAgent.contactinfo: Unisphere Networks, Inc. Postal: 10 Technology Park Drive Westford, MA 01886 USA Tel: +1 978 589 5800 E-mail: mib@UnisphereNetworks.com
usdIsisAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the intermediate system to intermediate system (IS-IS) protocol management component of the SNMP agent in the Unisphere Data Routing Switch family of products.

usdIsisAgentV1.name: usdIsisAgentV1
usdIsisAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the IS-IS component of the Unisphere Routing Switch SNMP
        agent.  This version of the IS-IS component was supported in the
        Unisphere RX 2.x system releases.
usdIsisAgentV1.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the intermediate system to intermediate system (IS-IS) protocol application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when the usdIsisCircState object was added.

usdIsisAgentV2.name: usdIsisAgentV2
usdIsisAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the IS-IS component of the Unisphere Routing Switch SNMP
        agent.  This version of the IS-IS component was supported in the
        Unisphere RX 3.x system releases.
usdIsisAgentV2.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the intermediate system to intermediate system (IS-IS) protocol application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when MPLS support was added.

usdIsisAgentV3.name: usdIsisAgentV3
usdIsisAgentV3.productrelease:
Version 3 of the IS-IS component of the Unisphere Routing Switch SNMP
        agent.  This version of the IS-IS component is supported in the
        Unisphere RX 4.0 and subsequent system releases.
usdIsisAgentV3.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the intermediate system to intermediate system (IS-IS) protocol application in the Unisphere Routing Switch.
